snippet.title: Awesomenauts Assemble! - Xbox One Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Awesomenauts Assemble! is now available on Xbox One! Join millions of players around the word and become one of the best intergalactic mercenaries in the known universe!

For more information, head over to Awesomenauts.com/ or visit the Xbox Website: https://store.xbox.com/en-GB/Xbox-One/Games/Awesomenauts-Assemble/4286d417-522e-4374-973c-4e048048ea03
